_sText: Eclipse ______________________________________ Made by Paper-Cut. Skybox by Paper-Cut. Jail concept by Paper-Cut, Jail scripting by Turkey Eater. ______________________________________ This map developed when I figured out how to make complex ramps, and pretty much showcases them throughout the entire level. Players start with no weapons, and depending on how well they surf, they will get better weapons. It is suggested that you do not run this on a DM server, as a lot of the functions were made specifically for a normal surf. We have a DM version in the works, and it should be out sometime soon. ______________________________________ This map was made specifically for 66tick. It will NOT function correctly on 100tick, so don't come here complaining when you try it. ______________________________________ Install: Put the bsp into cstrike/maps folder. ______________________________________ Thanks goes out to: FAJ, for ideas along the way. Target Practice, for various help along the way. Etrigan, for ideas and testing SintaxError, for pretty much everything. [UDEL]Steve, for unlocking the door of the awesome ramps. Turkey Eater, for pretty much everything. You rock man. _______________________________________ Visit Solidsurf.info for more great surf maps and surf mapping tutorials.
